WEBVTT

00:02:29.667 --> 00:02:34.684
Kasimama mbele ya kibubu akiwa amenyanyua nyundo hewani.

00:02:34.708 --> 00:02:36.958
Alikuwa anajiandaa kuiba pesa zangu

00:02:37.667 --> 00:02:38.976
Unajua,

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:41.476
mjomba wangu Freeman alikuwa mtu anayefahamu fani nyingi.

00:02:41.500 --> 00:02:42.851
Angerekebisha kitu yoyote-

00:02:42.875 --> 00:02:45.059
kiti kilichovinjika, chungu imepasuka-

00:02:45.083 --> 00:02:48.351
hata kurudisha uhai
kwa mimea za nyanya

00:02:48.375 --> 00:02:52.476
Alikua na sihiri
na vitu vilivyovunjika

00:02:52.500 --> 00:02:54.184
na watu wenye kasoro

00:02:54.208 --> 00:02:56.184
Angenichukua akienda kazini

00:02:56.208 --> 00:02:57.518
na kusema, "Kuja Jo,

00:02:57.542 --> 00:03:00.893
tukafanye kitu
kuibadili huu ulimwengu kua bora."